								<div class="tab-pane  js-equalheight-element" id="tab_amt_im_berblick_846888092">
									<h2 class="sr-only visible-print-block">The FOITT in brief</h2>
									<div class="row">
										
										




<div class="mod mod-teaser">



    
    
        
            
            
                <div class="col-sm-7">
                    <a href="/bit/en/home/foitt/the-foitt-in-brief.html" data-skipextcss="true"><img src="/bit/en/home/foitt/the-foitt-in-brief/_jcr_content/image.imagespooler.jpg/1538460076148/gebeaude-zollikofen.jpg" alt="Geb&#228;ude Standort Zollikofen"/></a>
                </div>
                <div class="col-sm-5 nopadding-left">
                    
                    
                        
                            <h4>
                                <a href="/bit/en/home/foitt/the-foitt-in-brief.html" title="The FOITT in brief " data-skipextcss="true">The FOITT in brief </a>
                            </h4>
                        
                        
                    
                    <p>In this age of communication, information technology is ever more present in our everyday lives. Industry, trade, transport, the armed forces, media and the leisure sector are dependent upon very complex and ingenious IT and telecommunications systems. Modern countries also make use of the latest technologies. The FOITT provides services for the Federal Administration, cantons, communes and other organisations.</p>

                    
                </div>
            

            
            
        
    

</div>



    
        
    



									</div>
								</div>
							

								

								

								<div class="tab-pane  js-equalheight-element" id="tab_eisbrecher_880176216">
									<h2 class="sr-only visible-print-block">Eisbrecher</h2>
									<div class="row">
										
										




<div class="mod mod-teaser">



    
    
        
            
            
                <div class="col-sm-7">
                    <a href="/bit/de/home/dokumentation/kundenzeitschrift-eisbrecher.html" data-skipextcss="true"><img src="/bit/de/home/dokumentation/kundenzeitschrift-eisbrecher/_jcr_content/image.imagespooler.png/1545206347083/eb-teaser-pp.png" alt="eb-teaser-pp"/></a>
                </div>
                <div class="col-sm-5 nopadding-left">
                    
                    
                        
                            <h4>
                                <a href="/bit/de/home/dokumentation/kundenzeitschrift-eisbrecher.html" title="Eisbrecher Customer magazine  " data-skipextcss="true">Eisbrecher Customer magazine  </a>
                            </h4>
                        
                        
                    
                    <p>The Eisbrecher is the FOITT's customer magazine which is published every three months. In the Eisbrecher you can find out more about the FOITT's projects and products, get tips and tricks on the federal IT system and read about what the FOITT is currently working on.</p>
<p><b>available in <a href="/bit/de/home/dokumentation/kundenzeitschrift-eisbrecher.html">German</a> and <a href="/bit/fr/home/documentation/le-magazine-eisbrecher.html">French</a></b></p>

                    
                </div>
            

            
            
        
    

</div>



    
        
    



									</div>
								</div>
							
						</div>
					</div>
				
			
		
	
</div>


