                                    <a href="/bit/de/home/subsites/herzlich-willkommen-bei-der-berufsbildung-bit.html" title="For learners" data-skipextcss="true">For learners</a>
                                </h3>
                            
                            
                        
                        <p>Are you choosing a career? There are over 80 IT career trainees in the FOITT undergoing training. These pages will tell you all about apprenticeships in the Federal Office of Information Technology, Systems and Telecommunication FOITT.</p>

                        
